1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
What if your body had a memory that could save your life?

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:09,200
After an infection or vaccine, your immune system creates memory cells.

3
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:12,400
These cells, like vigilant guards, remember past invaders.

4
00:00:12,400 --> 00:00:17,600
Memory B cells churn out antibodies, while memory T cells seek and destroy.

5
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:22,000
Together, they create a powerful defense, ready for the next attack.

6
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:24,400
Wondering how long this memory lasts?

7
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,400
Months, years, even a lifetime!

8
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:28,400
Curious about your immune system?

9
00:00:28,400 --> 00:00:31,200
Like and follow for more science secrets!
